videos.description: James Harden sends an outlet pass to Trevor Ariza who finishes at the rim with a sweet two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Harden finds Ariza for slam) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden finds Ariza for slam

videos.description: Clint Capela receives the lob from James Harden and throws down a two-handed jam early in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Harden feeds Capela for the flush) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden feeds Capela for the flush

videos.description: James Harden sends an impressive behind-the-back pass to Joe Johnson who scores a basket from deep.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Harden's no-look dish leads to 3) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden's no-look dish leads to 3

videos.description: James Harden scores 17 points in the first quarter to help the Rockets lead the Nuggets 38-25.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Harden lights up the 1st quarter) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden lights up the 1st quarter

videos.description: Mason Plumlee cuts through two defenders to receive the pass from Jamal Murray and then throws down the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Plumlee gets loose for alley-oop slam) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Plumlee gets loose for alley-oop slam

videos.description: James Harden knocks down a 3-pointer and gets fouled for his second 4-point play attempt in the first half against the Nuggets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Harden scores and-1 triple) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden scores and-1 triple

videos.description: James Harden dominates the first half against the Nuggets by scoring 27 points, including five baskets from behind the arc.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Harden's impressive 27-point first half) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden's impressive 27-point first half

videos.description: Nikola Jokic tries to defend James Harden but he hits the step-back jumper from deep and scores a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Harden scores triple over Jokic) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden scores triple over Jokic

videos.description: Chris Paul connects with Luc Mbah a Moute who breezes down the lane and finishes with an easy two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play ( Mbah a Moute throws it down) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mbah a Moute throws it down

videos.description: A fan gets his 15 minutes of fame when he catches the ball out of bounds before Trevor Ariza gets to it and the crowd lights up in excitement.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Nuggets praise fan that grabs loose ball) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nuggets praise fan that grabs loose ball

videos.description: James Harden hits the long jumper and scores his 41st point of the game with less than one minute remaining in regulation against the Nuggets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Rockets applaud Harden after 41-point effort) 2018/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rockets applaud Harden after 41-point effort
